text: Rhinestone is a 1984 American musical comedy movie directed by Bob Clark and starring Sylvester Stallone, Dolly Parton, Richard Farnsworth, Ron Leibman. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox and was a box office failure. ==Other websites== * * Category:1984 musical movies Category:1984 comedy movies Category:American musical comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Bob Clark
